OL,3,CManchester rolls out red carpet for
OL,4,CBRIT Awards 2026
OL,6,FMusic stars including Harry Styles,
OL,7,FRaye and Olivia Dean are set to
OL,8,Fdescend Manchester as the city gears
OL,9,Fup to host the first BRIT Award
OL,10,Fceremony held outside of London for
OL,11,Fthe first time in its history.
OL,13,FThe Co-op Live will play host to the
OL,14,Fbiggest and brightest in the industry
OL,15,Ffrom around the globe with
OL,16,Fperformances from Raye, rock band Wolf
OL,17,FAlice, and American singer-songwriter
OL,18,FSombr, whose real name is Shane Boose.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
