OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772386496
OL,3,CManchester rolls out red carpet for
OL,4,CBRIT Awards 2026
OL,6,FOne Direction star Harry Styles will
OL,7,Falso take to the stage to perform
OL,8,Fmusic from his upcoming fourth studio
OL,9,Falbum - Kiss All The Time, Disco,
OL,10,FOccasionally.
OL,12,FIt comes three years after his last
OL,13,Fperformance on the Brits' stage in
OL,14,F2023, which saw him take home four
OL,15,Fgongs following the release of his
OL,16,Falbum Harry's House.
OL,18,FLola Young and Olivia Dean lead the
OL,19,Fnominations, with a special
OL,20,Frecognition also promised for Oasis'
OL,21,FNoel Gallagher.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
