PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772386496
OL,3,CManchester rolls out red carpet for
OL,4,CBRIT Awards 2026
OL,6,FDean, 26, is nominated for artist and
OL,7,Falbum of the year, pop act, and has
OL,8,Ftwo chances at winning song of the
OL,9,Fyear for Man I Need and Rein Me In,
OL,10,Fthe latter thanks to a guest spot with
OL,11,FSam Fender.
OL,13,FYoung, 25, who won a Grammy this year
OL,14,Fin the best pop solo performance
OL,15,Fcategory for her hit song Messy, is up
OL,16,Ffor best pop act, artist of the year,
OL,17,Fbreakthrough act, best alternative and
OL,18,Frock act and best song.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
