CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772386496
OL,3,CManchester rolls out red carpet for
OL,4,CBRIT Awards 2026
OL,6,FElsewhere, Britpop band Pulp have
OL,7,Fscored their first nomination in 30
OL,8,Fyears, in the best group category,
OL,9,Fwhile last year's Mercury Prize winner
OL,10,FFender has four nominations.
OL,12,FLily Allen, whose album West End Girl
OL,13,Fcaused a stir when it was released
OL,14,Flast year, is nominated in three
OL,15,Fcategories - for best album, artist of
OL,16,Fthe year, and pop act.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
