PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772386496
OL,3,CManchester rolls out red carpet for
OL,4,CBRIT Awards 2026
OL,6,FAlex Warren's Ordinary is competing
OL,7,Fwith US popstars including Taylor
OL,8,FSwift, Chappell Roan, Gracie Abrams
OL,9,Fand Sabrina Carpenter in the
OL,10,Finternational song of the year
OL,11,Fcategory.
OL,13,FAdvance winners already announced
OL,14,Finclude Oasis's Noel Gallagher, who
OL,15,Fwill be named songwriter of the year,
OL,16,Fwhile record producer and DJ Ronson
OL,17,Fwill be honoured with the outstanding
OL,18,Fcontribution to music award.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
