OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772386496
OL,3,CManchester rolls out red carpet for
OL,4,CBRIT Awards 2026
OL,6,FSinger-songwriter PinkPantheress,
OL,7,Fwhose real name is Victoria Walker, is
OL,8,Fthe recipient of this year's Producer
OL,9,Fof the Year Award.
OL,11,FThe 24-year-old is the first woman and
OL,12,Fyoungest ever artist to win the
OL,13,Faccolade, according to the Brit Awards.
OL,15,FThe ceremony will be hosted by
OL,16,Fcomedian and actor Jack Whitehall and
OL,17,Fwill be broadcast on ITV and ITVX at
OL,18,F8.15pm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
